'''Greeklish''' or '''[[Latinoellinika]]''' ('''[[Λατινοελληνικά]]''') is the [[Latin]]-alphabet [[transliteration]] of [[Greek language]].

Commonly used in the [[Internet]].

Two forms:

==[[Phonetic]] Greeklish==
Where, for example, [[Νίκη]] is transliterated as [[Niki]].

==[[Orthographic]] Greeklish==
Where, for example, [[Νίκη]] is transliterated as [[Nikh]].

